american psycho is a 2000 american black comedy horror film co-written and directed by mary harron , based on bret easton ellis 's 1991 novel of the same name . it stars christian bale , willem dafoe , jared leto , josh lucas , chloÃ« sevigny , samantha mathis , cara seymour , justin theroux , and reese witherspoon . producer edward r. pressman purchased the film rights to the novel in 1992 . after discussions with david cronenberg fell through , harron was brought on to direct and cast bale in the lead role . lionsgate acquired worldwide distribution in 1997 and temporarily replaced harron and bale with oliver stone as director and leonardo dicaprio portraying patrick bateman . dicaprio left in favor of the beach and harron and bale were brought back . american psycho debuted at the sundance film festival on january 21 , 2000 , and was released theatrically on april 14 , 2000 . the film received generally positive reviews and was a financial success , with critics mainly praising the screenplay and christian bale 's performance .